-- Aurora Suspect Told Classmate He Wanted to Kill, Prosecutors Say
-- B y   A n d r e w   D u n n
-- 2012-08-24T19:00:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-24/aurora-suspect-told-classmate-he-wanted-to-kill-prosecutors-say.html
James Holmes, the man accused of
shooting 12 people to death last month at a movie theater in
Aurora, Colorado, had conversations with a classmate in March
about wanting to kill people, according to a court filing by
prosecutors dated Aug. 14 and made public today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
